&lt;div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
&lt;div class="w-100" >&lt;img src="https://axell-de.github.io/pr-preview/5/img/newform-editformat.jpg" alt="Antwortenformat" loading="lazy" data-zoomable />&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
